Product name: Dave Ramsey Envelope System, Dave Ramsey Wallet, GREY, Cash Envelope Wallet, Cash System Wallet, Cash Envelope System Wallet,
Description:
**PLEASE READ ENTIRE DESCRIPTION BEFORE ORDERING! BY PURCHASING YOU ARE AGREEING THAT YOU READ THE ENTIRE FOLLOWING DESCRIPTION and POLICIES.**
Tired of your change falling out of your paper envelopes? Your paper envelopes falling apart and making keeping track of your budget difficult and stressful? Solve the problem with this cash system wallet! 
Half our life has been lived in Japan over the last 5 years so naturally parts of my creative process become influenced - I introduce you to our Sakura wallet! This wallet is made from beautifully coordinating cherry blossom and polka dot oil cloth, it is waterproof! Each pocket is equipped with a clear vinyl label pocket where you can slip a piece of paper to label each budget section. Zippers alternating sides for easy accessibility. Wallet measures roughly 7.5" x 3.5" with thickness dependent on number of pockets (4pkt= 1", 6pkt= 1.5" , 8pkt= 2"; wallet will compress with use, this is the thicken caused by the stacking of zippers at the top of the wallet that will not give with time) when folded as a wallet. Wallet contains your choice of 4, 6, or 8 zipped pockets to hold cash and coins and closes with velcro (please read below as to why velcro is the best closure option for these oil cloth wallets).
Wallets have the option to be made with a card holding section; 5 card pockets total which includes one clear pocket suggested to be used for ID. This costs an extra 12 and is noted by 'w/ Card Slots' when selecting wallet variation to purchase in the dropdown menu on the right. 
Due to being made-to-order actual wallet received may look slightly different due to cuts of patterned fabric but very close and still high quality work.
Wallet has a 2-3 week processing time but most orders are finished and shipped under a week, just depends on current volume of made-to-order orders. 
SHIPPING POLICY:
All orders will ship from Japan post in Yokosuka, Japan. Delivery from Japan to the United States typically takes 7-10 days; if expedited shipping is desired please message before purchase. When shipping to all other overseas countries, customs can delay packages by up to 6 weeks. This doesn't happen often, but it can happen. No tracking is provided unless purchased by customer as a shipping upgrade. Root & Blossom is not held responsible for lost or stole mail; see 'Refund and Exchanges' section in policy for more information. 
If the shipping address is different from the address provided through Etsy, please contact the seller prior to payment. Root & Blossom will send the order to the address provided through Etsy whether or not it passes through the verification process.
Additional FAQs:
Why Velcro? Customers often times asks for a closure other than velcro or suggest a different type of closure in their reviews. Velcro is indeed the most suitable closure for this type of material - inserting a clasp, snap, or button would compromise the oil cloth and would most likely result in a rip/tear over time. Velco is the most durable match to oil cloth. 
If you're purchasing a Root & Blossom item as a gift, special packaging and a hand written note can be included at no extra cost. Please use the "contact the seller" link at the bottom of the page to inform us of the occasion, shipping address, and personal message to be included in the package.

Description:
This Gift Set Includes:
- 1 Bandana Bib
- 1 Burp Cloth
- 1 Organic Maple Wood Teether
- 1 Coordinating Knot Bow (see photos)
For Monogramming:  In "notes to seller" at checkout, please provide initials in the order you would like them along with font and thread choice.  Please note: Full names are available only for burp cloths.
*Traditionally, girls monograms read First, Last, Middle with the Last name initial bigger than the other two. 
*Traditionally, boys monograms read First, Middle, Last in block letters all the same size. 
~Bandana Bib~
The stylish bandana bib is made out of 100% cotton fabric backed with soft and absorbent cotton chenille.  This bib is secured by two sets of sturdy Kam snaps which allow baby to wear it from birth up to 3 years of age. Because this bandana bib is soft and lightweight, it is great for feedings or as an all day drool catcher!
~Contoured Burp Cloth~
Made from 100% cotton backed with cotton chenille, the contoured shape fits your shoulder comfortably while providing a soft surface for baby. These are not only super stylish and adorable, but they are also very practical and versatile.  They can be used from burping your baby to wiping messy toddler hands and faces - and they will last that long - through many, many washes!
~Organic Maple Wood Teether~
The adorable teether made out of organic maple wood is sure to ease sore little gums and entertain at the same time.  Wooden ring is made out of maple wood and brushed with organic beeswax to keep the wood from splintering.  No harsh chemicals were used in the production process, making it a great alternative to plastic/synthetic baby teethers.  The ring can be easily attached to a pacifier clip to keep it from getting lost.
Soft bunny ears are made out of absorbent terry cloth and 100% cotton. They are great for baby to hold onto and munch on. They can be easily removed to be washed or even placed in the freezer for a few minutes while damp to cool.
~Knot Bow~
The knot bow comes on either a one-size-fits-all nylon headband or a no-slip-grip alligator clip (you get to choose at checkout).
~Dimensions~
-Bib Neck Opening is adjustable from 10" to 14" (newborn to 3 years)
-Teething Ring: 3" in diameter
-Contoured Burp Cloths: 19" long, 8" at widest 
~Suggested Care Instructions~
-Wipe organic maple wood with a damp cloth
-Remove cotton bunny ears and machine wash cold, tumble dry low
-Bibs/Burp Cloths can be machine washed cold, tumble dry low
-All items are pre-washed using organic baby detergent and dried
All of my items are handmade with lots of love to order in a smoke-free studio.  A portion of each sale is donated to Newborns In Need. 
**Always supervise your baby when wearing a bib and remove for sleeping**

Description:
The Parlor Apothecary's potion necklace allows you to choose from any of our charming victorian eau de perfumes. The perfume is poured inside a beautiful glass amulet, a heart shaped vial, containing 4ml of delicate perfume. Choose from gold or silver.
This darling pendant hangs from a 26" chain with lobster clasp closure. The bottle pendant measures 46mm x 33mm (1.8 inches x 1.3 inches). Great for travel- to apply, gently dab a small amount of perfume to pulse points as often as you fancy. 
You may also choose to purchase this necklace without perfume, please select "none" from the drop down menu at checkout. 
The color of perfume contained may vary depending on your fragrance of choice- as the colors are different for each. The color is listed beside the name in the scent descriptions below, please note.
Arrives tucked inside a muslin satchel and custom gift box with gift tag.
Choose your scent: 
~ ::: SCENT DESCRIPTIONS ::: ~
- ALCHEMY ELIXIR ™ - (Light Pink)
An enchanting floral scent with warm and woodsy notes of amber, sandalwood and vanilla layered with sparkling hints of fruity florals like citrus, apricot and raspberry. 
- MADEMOISELLE SPIRIT ™ - (Gold)
 A fragrance that  should be worn by the most enchanting of ladies. Fresh peach is blended with woodsy notes of sandalwood and an undertone of sweet vanilla and crisp grapefruit make this a simply darling and feminine scent. 
- LINGERIE MIST ™ - (Peach)
A fresh and flirty fragrance which softens the heart and soul. Brown sugar cane mixed with notes of amber and vanilla creates a sexy sweet aroma. The perfect scent for lounging about in lacy knickers. 
- VICTORIAN SPIRIT ™ - (Gold)
A fragrance evoking the mystery of times past . Woodland notes of amber blended with creamy vanilla and apricot create a warm and sweet aroma with a an earthy undertone.
- DAMSEL BOUQUET ™ - (Light Pink)
A delicate and feminine fragrance perfect for wearing to tea. Sweet rose petals blended with creamy vanilla create a sweet aroma with a ladylike allure. 
- VELVET TONIC ™ - (Brown)
A sophisticatedly sweet scent. Warm and woody madagascar vanilla and sandalwood layered with exotic floral notes of plumeria, clementine and heliotrope make this a sensual love potion.
- VIOLETTE TINCTURE ™ - (Purple)
An enchanting fragrance like wandering through a secret garden. Delicate notes of violet flowers blended with soft vanilla and lavender create a sweet aroma with a ladylike allure. 
- ABSINTHE TONIC ™ - (Green)
A fragrance which promotes good luck and cleansing. Spicy notes of clove blended with refreshing bergamot citrus and subtle hints of sweet rose and fresh lavender. Inspired by the famous "florida water" cologne of the 1800's. 
- WANDERLUST PARFUM ™ - (Clear)
A girlish fragrance with a whimsical twist. Sugared strawberries frosted with crisp vanilla cream and sweet petals create a delicious aroma.
- FAIRYTALE MIST ™ - (Clear)
A soft velvety scent with a magical aroma. This feminine fragrance has sugary cotton candy layered with notes of creamy vanilla- creating a charming ladylike fragrance. 
- LOVELY LADY ™ - (Clear)
A flirty fragrance for mademoiselles. Sweet cream is layered with notes of sugared rose petals and warm springtime florals, creating a delicately charming yet coy mystique. 
- ANTIQUE TONIC ™ - (Clear)
A calming fragrance which relaxes the senses . A cool mist of french lavender blended with notes of sweet vanilla creates a velvety soft aroma. This is a delicate concoction evoking feminine allure.
- TOBACCO TONIC ™ - (Gold) 
An aged and old fashioned fragrance. Fresh notes of tobacco flower, amber and leather are blended with a hint vanilla and orange to create a sweet aroma with rich history.
- PETTICOAT LACE ™ - (Clear)
Petticoat Lace is an enchanting floral scent with exotic notes of gardenia, blossoming rose, and a wink of bergamot and vanilla to make it fresh and flirty. This scent evokes the romantic feelings of falling in love. Put on a pretty dress, paint your nails, enjoy being a girl.

Product name: Montessori Multi Sensory PlayDough Basket
Description:
Montessori Sensorial Work, Waldorf Sensory Play, Reggio Emilia 
Mindful/Peaceful Playdough
I designed this Multi-Sensory PlayDough Basket to encourage peace, tranquility, and mindfulness through creative hands on play and exploration.
Children can use the mortar and pestle to grind the calming dried lavender and chamomile and then add their mix to the dough for texture and scent. I have also included laminated identification cards to extend literacy and language.
The flower press doubles as a round cutter and represents new beginnings, balance and harmony. The hummingbird symbolizes joy and playfulness, as well as adaptability, lightness of being, enjoyment of life, being present, independence, and lifting up negativity. Together the flower and humming bird represent the delicate symbiotic relationship in nature, each relying on each other to survive.
I often bring this set out during quiet time in the afternoon or in the evening before bed.
I have also included four tools for cutting and shaping the dough and a small wooden rolling pin. These tools will help develop hand strength, fine motor skills, and coordination, You will also receive 8 oz Homemade PlayDough in an air tight container and the recipe.

Product name: Webcam Cover for Privacy Open or Close with just one simple finger movement
Description:
Privacy and Peace of Mind is the utmost concern nowadays with all the electronic devices we carry. Everyone I know is concerned with the little camera in our devices and wonder if it is spying on us. The fact of the matter is that it is entirely possible. If our computer or mobile devices are infected with malware, the programmed code can easily use the Operating Systems features via API calls and query the camera allowing someone to watch without us ever suspecting anything. Take for instance the cross-platform malware Backdoor.Mokes.a, which is able to run on Linux to Windows to Apple's OS X and is able to activate our computer's webcam. Even the world's most powerful law enforcement agency's director James Comey (FBI) stated that he places a cover over his camera and says "there’s some sensible things you should be doing, and that’s one of them … You do that so that people who don’t have authority don’t look at you. I think that’s a good thing."
Covering our webcam isn’t a substitute for keeping your systems patched via software updates and running effective anti-virus (although anti-virus is useless against sophisticated trojans and rootkits) but, if you’re doing both those things, it’s another layer of in depth that’s worth considering and easy to apply.
Still need convincing? Then use your favorite search engine and search for Insecam, a site that shows thousands of feeds from private cameras throughout the world. Creepy right?
CloakCam webcam covers will protect the camera of your laptop, tablet, smartphone or other technical devices from hacker attacks and can be opened or closed with just one simple finger movement. The 3M adhesive can be easily applied and removed from the required device without trace. I guarantee once cloakCAM is applied you will never remove it. Why would you if you are able to open or close the webcam lens with just one simple finger movement?
Take control of your digital privacy with CloakCAM.
Our webcam covers are of the highest quality and are available in Metal (high quality steel available in black and silver) or Color Cloak (robust polycarbonate available in various colors). These beautiful high quality, not to mention VERY classy-looking, privacy covers will not disappoint you. I should know; my family uses them too and feel safe in front of their webcams. Our devices even look stylish and classy with them while protecting us.
Protect yourself and your family with CloakCAM.
Product Features: 
PROTECTS YOUR SECURITY AND PRIVACY: Covers your webcam when not in use and prevents webcam hackers from spying on you. Slides open when you need to use your webcam. Locks in place to ensure cover does not slide open. 
EXTREMELY THIN AND DURABLE: Measuring only 1.3mm thick, will not interfere with closing your laptop. Adheres with double sided 3M tape, can be removed if needed but will stay on strong through wear and tear. 
FITS ON MOST DEVICES: Can be used to cover most webcams on phones, laptops, and tablets. Does not interfere with webcam use or indicator light.

We have three available designs (please see listing photos). Please feel feel free to send us a message if you want a custom order.
To order, please provide the following:
1.  DATE you need the order.  Our processing time is 2 weeks, but send us a message if you need it sooner.
2.  DESIGN
3.  MONOGRAM or INITIAL - For monograms, please send how you want it printed. Please see below for monogramming guidelines.
*MONOGRAM GUIDELINES:
Here are a few general guidelines for monogramming to make it easier for you:
For a Married Couple (or soon to be):
The monogram will contain the bride's first initial, the surname of the couple, and the groom's first initial, in that order. For instance Jennifer and Kyle Smith will be JSK
Monogramming a Gift for a Woman:
A monogrammed gift for a woman should include her first, middle and last initial or if she is married, her first, maiden name, and married name initials. Traditionally, a woman's monogram is presented in first, last, middle initial order. So for Gabriella Marie Smith, it will be GSM
Monogramming a Gift for a Man:
For men's gifts, it is very important to consider the shape of the item to be monogrammed when choosing the order of the initials. When monogramming something for a man, many people prefer to use the initials in the first, middle and last order when all the letters are the same height. For example, Robert John West will be RJW (all letters same height). Or when the letter in the middle is bigger, you can use the same tips for a woman - first, last and middle initials (Robert John West's will be RWJ if the middle is taller than the other two initials)

HOW TO .... BRACELET SIZE :
Measure the wrist below the wrist bone, where you will wear your bracelet, using a strip of paper. 
Mark your strip with a pen where the end of the bracelet needs to be. 
Measure the paper strip with a ruler. This is your wrist size.
Increase the wrist measurement based on how you want the bracelet to fit :
a snug fit : add 1/4 inch to 1/2 inch
a comfort fit : add 3/4 inch to 1 inch
a loose fit : add 1 1/4 inch

Description:
Black Tourmaline Rings | Rough Black Tourmaline | Electroform Rings | Crystal Rings | Black Tourmaline and Copper | Boho Ring | Stone Ring
Black tourmaline is one of the best crystals to use against negativity of all kinds. It's a very popular stone and for good reason, it's really powerful and it works! 
Whether you want to feel grounded to the Earth (being a base chakra stone) or protected against negative energies, bad moods, crummy people, stressful work environments, stressful schedules and general bad vibes, keeping black tourmaline close by is a must.

The rings are made with premium quality raw black tourmaline rods, straight from the earth. Some are double terminated. All are special. They average between 10 - 15 mm.
They are electroformed with copper, which is a slow process where copper is deposited around the stone forming the ring. It can take 8-12 hours for this to happen. They are then cleaned, polished, and a thin layer of wax is added for temporary protection. You can also choose from having aged/antiqued or bare copper. The photos show aged copper.
